{"tid":1702811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國戰線] 所有喺香港嘅美國公民同我入嚟!! 遙距寄Postcard俾國會議員!","createTime":"2019-11-10T02:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T03:54:39.000Z","uid":224007,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bc12201a5227b6adcd9267c744d6db4b7e34a19b","tid":1702811,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"各位，又係我哋HKHRDA Postcard團隊！林鄭政府之暴政，香港黑警之暴行，香港人已經無得再退 !! 我們一群居美香港人繼續積極推動美國國會儘快通過《香港人權及民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n自從十月初我們推出明信片游說計劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">在一個月內已在美國本土寄出超過6,800張明信片</span>。由於反應理想，我們現希望將HKHRDA Postcard campaign 推至身在香港的美國人。<br />\n<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》在十月十五日順利過了第一關，在美國眾議院通過，現在到了第二關參議院卻出現暗湧。面對中美貿易談判和中國反游說，我們亦轉打持久民意戰，務求令 Co-sponsor 數目與日俱增，在美國朝野的立法壓力只會有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們促請現居於香港的美國公民出一分力，如果你支持《香港人權及民主法案》，可在以下表格提供資料(<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/HKHRDApostcard-overseas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2FHKHRDApostcard-overseas&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=6f253af8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/HKHRDApostcard-overseas</a>)，我們會按照你在美國的地址 , 代你寄 &rdquo;Vote YES H.R. 3289 and S. 1838 Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&rdquo; 明信片給你所屬州份的參議員。(註：只要是美國公民，未成年人士亦享有同等請願權，也可以出一分力為香港爭取求援！)<br />\n<br />\n如果想跟進我哋HKHRDA Postcard Campaign 的進展，可以follow:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Postcard.HKHRDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPostcard.HKHRDA%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c790af70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Postcard.HKHRDA/</a>. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BOSstandswithHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBOSstandswithHK%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=46d50c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BOSstandswithHK/</a><br />\n如果想贊助明信片游說計劃，可到此網頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://postcardhkhrda.wixsite.com/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostcardhkhrda.wixsite.com%2Fdonate&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=cea28bec\" target=\"_blank\">https://postcardhkhrda.wixsite.com/donate</a>.<br />\n<br />\n附圖為截至11月4號已寄出明信片的分布圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1shgyMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1shgyMP.png&h=3ed229c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1: Front of Postcard (download the original file at the link below for printing, don&rsquo;t use this)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9aekr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9aekr1.png&h=0dd332f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLtjwyJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLtjwyJ.png&h=9ca85241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgH00r5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwgH00r5.png&h=b18fc725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffWpHFr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffWpHFr.png&h=8a7b379e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2: Back of Postcard (download the original file at the link below for printing, don&rsquo;t use this)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugtvDeg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugtvDeg.png&h=5f3f5540&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2e2aa7c80c1642ffc712fe768228f80f07889fc","tid":1702811,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"支持呀"},{"pid":"fc06b9209088cae6f22df3ba702f475675c609ed","tid":1702811,"uid":156096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先58%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=91abdcfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=dfbf096f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244f622e37bfee7d36d23347d31d467563a999e5","tid":1702811,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"人在大阪推一推"},{"pid":"d31f330cd0a3493214d0634599329dd4ad45bb57","tid":1702811,"uid":321684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁照推"},{"pid":"235d50e5fc02b92199ab48b03e3a60a9ea542cfd","tid":1702811,"uid":321684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-